sys_user_role.description: This role provides all of the same access granted by the license_owner role. This role also grants access to workspace development and configuration through tools such as UI Builder. This role was created so that it could be assigned to a member of the License Owner's team rather than be restricted to the license_admin role. If there is no one on the License Owner's team that meets the requirements, this role should be filled by the license_owner or another platform developer. This role is split out from the admin role so that development can be delegated in a citizen development manner.
sys_user_role.name: x_881287_license_0.license_workspace_developer
